Here is your comprehensive **"Getting Started Manual"** for setting up a full-stack monorepo using Vue 3, Express (ESM + TypeScript), Terraform for GCP, Husky for pre-commit hooks, and pnpm workspaces. This guide provides an end-to-end blueprint with opinionated, modern best practices.

