## ðŸŽ¨ 1. Boilerplate Web App with Vue.js

```bash
mkdir apps && cd apps
pnpm create vue@latest web
# Choose TypeScript, Vite, Pinia, Vue Router, ESLint, Prettier, Vitest
cd web
pnpm add -D @vitest/coverage-v8
pnpm install
pnpm dev
mv .vscode ../../ && cd ../..
```

Add `// @ts-expect-error: no types available for flat config` for `eslint-plugin-cypress/flat` to avoid type
definition errors.

Add coverage output to `vitest.config.ts`:

```ts
export default mergeConfig(
  // ...
  defineConfig({
    test: {
      // ...
      coverage: {
        provider: "v8",
      },
    },
  })
);
```

Follow: [Vue 3 Quick Start](https://vuejs.org/guide/quick-start.html)

