## â˜ï¸ 3. Terraform for GCP (Cloud Run + API Gateway)

Create `terraform/` directory with:

```hcl
provider "google" {
  project = var.project_id
  region  = var.region
}

resource "google_cloud_run_service" "hello" {
  name     = "hello-service"
  location = var.region
  template {
    spec {
      containers {
        image = "gcr.io/${var.project_id}/hello-service"
      }
    }
  }
}

resource "google_api_gateway_api" "default" {
  api_id = "main-api"
}
```

Also add:

- `variables.tf`
- `outputs.tf`
- `backend.tf` for remote state (e.g., GCS)

Official guide: [Terraform Cloud Run](https://registry.terraform.io/providers/hashicorp/google/latest/docs/resources/cloud_run_service)

